1.0.0.0  2026-03-09  Initial MSIX release
  - Two-process architecture (App tray UI + Service background sync)
  - JMAP FileNode sync with SSE push notifications
  - On-demand hydration and dehydration (cfapi cloud files)
  - Thumbnail provider (native C DLL via COM SurrogateServer)
  - Content URI source for web preview links
  - Explorer nav pane integration with cloud status icons
  - OAuth and app password authentication
  - Progressive hydration with range requests
  - Recycle bin support (trash role)
  - Auto-start on login via MSIX startup tasks
